column5: Our little angle  Shi,turned 1 today. She enjoyed a small turkey burger made just to her likeing and some tater salad. Then it was show time. Bring in the cake.LOL   Ah does this bring back memories of our firsts with the boys.   Birthday girl    Now for the fun.          Ok dad,shes all yours now.     Happy birthday little one.  Poppy and Nanny.
yeah it does bring back memories  seems most kids have to eat cake that way
We have pictures like that around here somewhere. Great eh? Thanks for the post. Jim
Some Dad you are, posting topless pics of your daughter on the internet. She is cute though... Mine were cuter, but not bad.
My first is now 17 days old... - things to look forward to haha
